Class BiomedicalEquipment

java.lang.Object
com.prototype.model.entities.Equipment
com.prototype.model.entities.BiomedicalEquipment
@Entity public class BiomedicalEquipment extends Equipment
Entity that represents a biomedical equipment item registered in the system.

This class extends Equipment and adds fields specific to biomedical devices, such as risk classification and calibration certification. These attributes provide the necessary traceability required for biomedical equipment inside institutional environments.

Instances are stored in the biomedical_equiments table.
